{
  "stem": "14292.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a big library, actually, at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was available, you know, literature from Greece, and-- Homers and English Shakespeare, and all this there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was very interested in Hungarian poetry and literature as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, maybe I was exposed to very little anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're talking about right now when I grew up as a young child, or even in the high school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Eventually, of course, at the end of the high school years, this became more and more influenced by the outside world, and-- such as, like, in Germany, what's happening and Austria occupied, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, of course, we became very aware of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For example, that not only you couldn't go to the university, but also it's, let's say, the university student was walking in front of the school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- and they started to scream, we want a country without Jews, and so forth!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was one of the slogans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was actually now in the early '40s.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, you see, the-- I was, in 1939, still in high school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I finished in 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as you know, in 1939, the war started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a lot of refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Hungarians were very unusual in this regard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- for example, they let the Polish Army to escape through Hungary and actually went to Africa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even so, they were on the side of the German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were exposed to, at that time, a little bit more of the reality of what's going on in Europe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think I remember him when he became a chancellor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I heard him many times to speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's a-- it's a very interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
